# MERN ToDoList

## Aim

The aim of this project is to create a todo list app that let's users keep track of their individual tasks.

## Stack

The project will be built with the MERN stak: Mongodb, Express, Node, and React.

## Requirements

### User login

Users will be able to create an account with authentication to be able to log in to see their tasks.

### Task CRUD

Users will be able to view their list of tasks, create new tasks, check or uncheck tasks, and delete old tasks.

### User CRUD

User will be able to view their account info, change their password or username, and delete their account.
